{"tid":645703,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"香港究竟邊度有好食既大福賣","createTime":"2018-04-28T11:46:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T09:45:37.000Z","uid":184194,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c0abfc6a88f764445874c476ee6241355aedba9a","tid":645703,"uid":184194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T11:46:27.000Z","msg":"是咁的。本人好鍾意食大福，去日本旅行一試難忘，日日食兩三個。但番到香港發現根本就冇士多啤梨大福賣。就算係普通大福都係包裝食品，唔係皮太厚就係d豆又鞋口又唔甜。東海堂果隻入面唔係紅豆。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人係香港食到好味既大福啊🙏🏻🙏🏻"},{"pid":"0b046a47b02ca58f9584c10aba439008d1957ead","tid":645703,"uid":21716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T11:47:59.000Z","msg":"A1"},{"pid":"b8d592f9556aca90e3f246ddc62840da568edc58","tid":645703,"uid":184194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T11:55:03.000Z","msg":"A1 bakery?"},{"pid":"46cbb038c6fc6ba3b124dfe7b7e33cd9f7e869f3","tid":645703,"uid":119393,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12:49:35.000Z","msg":"SOGO地庫"},{"pid":"33caf71bcd28a9f7f7d49b39fb5e20ee1d774479","tid":645703,"uid":184194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T16:36:30.000Z","msg":"urban?🤔"},{"pid":"48798fceb236847d5105e5fcfabf0cc4d9dd9069","tid":645703,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T17:06:14.000Z","msg":"糯米糍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25eb0a4f842b5a6df4fc8dccee121cf40b3e5afd","tid":645703,"uid":3896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T17:22:07.000Z","msg":"自己整啦, 以前返工同事整過 請我食<br />\n覺得好好食, 所有材料有得買 連紅豆蓉都有<br />\n之後自己包埋就得 佢話好簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"835577f0065efdc08eb710dc953a03d9b04caace","tid":645703,"uid":99883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sco